These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, paramedic
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, train
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the videographer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | photography       | singing |
| Job         | paramedic | videographer  |
| Sport       | rugby    | cricket    |
| Transport   | train       | ship      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up
The people have 2 different jobs:  freelancer, accountant
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: thriller, satire
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, baseball
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
2. the freelancer is on the far left##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | 7up     | hot-chocolate |
| Job           | freelancer | accountant      |
| Movie-Genre   | satire  | thriller      |
| Sport         | badminton | baseball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: pear, pepper
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, d&b
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, roller
1. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the roller##1
3. the person eating pear is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | cola | almond-milk  |
| Food          | pear    | pepper   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | blues   |
| Transport     | roller     | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade
There 2 different types of food: onion, banana
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, videographer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, funk
1. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | sprite       | lemonade |
| Food          | banana         | onion    |
| Job           | videographer | accountant    |
| Music-Genre   | salsa           | funk   |

