The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, dubstep
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, soccer
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, train
1. the fan of soul is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person driving the train##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | singing   |
| Music-Genre   | soul | dubstep       |
| Sport         | swimming   | soccer |
| Transport     | train    | scooter     |

