.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-10::.
There 2 different types of food: lettuce, banana
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, disco
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, spanish
2 different pets are kept: frog, snake
1. the spanish is the owner of the snake##1
2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
3. the spanish is on the right of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | lettuce | banana |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | disco      |
| Nationality   | russian | spanish    |
| Pet           | frog    | snake    |

