3. the owner of the ferret is the librarian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | librarian | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire          | zombie |
| Pet           | ferret          | pony    |
| Transport     | trike            | bike       |

 